{{Infobox company |name = Playmates |logo = Playmates Holdings Logo.png |logo_size = 226px |type = [[Listed company]] |foundation = 1966 |location_city = [[El Segundo, California]] |location_country = [[United States]] |location = |locations = |key_people = |area_served = |industry = [[Toy]] |products = [[Action figure]]s |services = |revenue = |operating_income = |net_income = |num_employees = |parent = |divisions = |subsid = |caption = |homepage = [http://www.playmatestoys.com PlaymatesToys.com] |dissolved = |footnotes = |intl = }} '''Playmates Toys''' ({{sehk|0869}}) is a [[El Segundo, California]] toy manufacturer and a subsidiary of [[Hong Kong]]-based '''Playmates Holdings Ltd''' ({{sehk2|0635}}). Founded in 1966, it is best known for their dolls, figurines and action figures, based on popular culture.
